>> ### Exponential Equations ### <<


Properties that can be useful in solving exponential equations are:

* [`\ln(b^a)=a \ln(b)`]
* [`\ln(ab) = \ln(a) + \ln(b)`]
* [`\ln \left(\displaystyle{\frac{a}{b}}\right)= \ln(a) - \ln(b)`]
* When [`a=b`] then [`\ln(a)=\ln(b)`].



>> ### Practice ### <<


